  "id": "BIT-nextcloud-2021-32658",
  "summary": "Sensitive data may not be removed from storage on account removal",
  "details": "Nextcloud Android is the Android client for the Nextcloud open source home cloud system. Due to a timeout issue the Android client may not properly clean all sensitive data on account removal. This could include sensitive key material such as the End-to-End encryption keys. It is recommended that the Nextcloud Android App is upgraded to 3.16.1",
